flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
It grips prey with its tail claws
and injects poison. It tenaciously
hangs on until the poison takes.

It lives in arid lands. It buries
itself in sand and lies in wait for
unsuspecting prey.

As soon as the tail claws close,
its needle tips secrete poison.
It can survive a year without food.

It burrows under the sand to lie in
wait for prey. Its tail claws can inject
its prey with a savage poison.

Dieses Pokmon vergrbt sich im Sand und
lauert dort regungslos seiner Beute auf. Es ist
artverwandt mit Thermopod.

After burrowing into the sand, it waits patiently
for prey to come near. This Pokmon and
Sizzlipede share common descent.

Il attaque avec les pinces empoisonnes
de sa queue. Le venin se rpand alors

Es schlgt mit den giftigen Krallen an seinem
Schweif zu. Wer von ihnen gestochen wird,

Ataca con las pinzas venenosas de la cola. Tras
clavarlas, inyecta una toxina que inmoviliza a la
presa.

Attacca la preda afferrandola con gli artigli
velenosi della coda, poi inietta il veleno per
immobilizzarla.

It attacks using the claws on its tail. Once locked
in its grip, its prey is unable to move as this
Pokmons poison seeps in.
